longBusinessSummary: Under normal circumstances, the fund invests at least 80% of its assets in equity securities of mid cap companies. Many of the equity securities in the fund's portfolio are securities of companies in the financials, industrials and consumer discretionary sectors. In managing the fund, the adviser employs a fundamental data science enabled investment approach that combines research, data insights, and risk management.
longName: JPMorgan Fundamental Data Science Mid Core ETF
